org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.asynch.finalmessage

Class FinalMessagesProcessingServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.asynch.finalmessage.FinalMessagesProcessingServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FinalMessagesProcessingService

    public class FinalMessagesProcessingServiceImpl
extends Object
implements FinalMessagesProcessingService
    Default implementation of FinalMessagesProcessingService. Does find messages in final states & configured last update time. After startup, fast check if all required params are filled is performed. Note: there is technical limit on how many messages for each state are processed at most. (CoreProps.ASYNCH_FINAL_MESSAGES_ITERATION_MESSAGE_LIMIT).
    Since:
    2.1
    Author:
    Karel Kovarik
